PREREQUISITES
*  Install unittest, tornado

CLONE REPOSITORY
* git clone https://github.com/cptlc/model-server.git
* cd model-server

CONFIGURE 
*  export PYTHONPATH=$PYTHONPATH:`pwd`/src
*  Edit config/tests.ini and config/server.ini
   Set 'model_basedir' to the clone of https://github.com/cptlc/cptl-models.git
*  Edit the contents of the 'keys' directory if necessary

RUN TESTS
* python src/cptl/test/daos_tests.py
* python src/cptl/test/requests_tests.py

GETTING STARTED 
* sudo python src/server.py
* Browse to http://localhost:443/
  



